%N A396162 First column of the triangular array with T(0, m) = m^m and T(n, m) = T(n - 1, m + 3) - 2*T(n - 1, m + 2) + T(n - 1, m + 1).
%C A396162 This sequence is obtained by iterating the shift-difference operator E*(E - 1)^2 on f(m) = m^m and evaluating at m = 0, where E is the shift operator.
%F A396162 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..2*n} (-1)^k*binomial(2*n, k)*(n + k)^(n + k), with 0^0 = 1.
